<L>__{exterior broadway night}
<A>__{cabs, daily news and times delivery trucks, bakery vans and a few cruising cabs, one or two passenger cars and a coasting green and black police cruiser this is the 4:30 a.m. traffic through which doyle moves. a rear window view of sal and angie boca, in animated conversation. his head is turned toward her, his hand raised in a gesture. angie is sitting in a corner with her back to the door, in profile to the back window. her blonde head bobbles with laughter over some remark sal has made. a long overhead view of the two cars wheeling in and out of the sparse traffic. close shot of the license plate on boca's car. close shot doyle staring at license plate, memorizing it.}
